title.narrative: 5. CROSS-SECTORAL APPROACHES

description.narrative: Strategies to address cross-cutting issues related to child rights are developed and applied., which contributes to Operations Support To Programme Delivery. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building, Systems Strengthening To Leave No One Behind. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: by 2022, the country programme is efficiently designed, coordinated and supported to meet quality programming standards in attaining the results in favour of the most marginalized children.
